snippet.title: Cruis'n Blast Vehicle Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out some of the vehicles that will be in the upcoming Cruis'n Blast for Nintendo Switch. Cruis'n Blast is getting a digital and physical release on Nintendo Switch September 14, 2021.


For more on the game, head here: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/cruisn-blast-switch/
